title: Bengal Fish Curry
Description: This is a traditional Bengali Fish recipe from West Bengal, India made with Bass fish with bones in and cooked with delicious spices from East 2 West Supply. The juicy spicy gravy goes very well with white rice and a must try dish.

title: Bengal Chicken Curry
Description: This is a traditional Bengali chicken curry and very flavorful chicken dish pairs perfectly with white rice or roti. Boneless and skinless chicken thigh is prepared with fresh, delicious, flavorful spices from East 2 West Supply.

title: Bhindi (Okra) Aloo Stir Fry-Vegetarian
Description: Bhindi (Okra) Aloo Stir Fry is a popular dish through out India. This is a vegetarian dish made with fresh & green Bhindi (Okra) and Potatoes lightly fried in cooking oil.

title: Spinach Paneer-Vegetarian
Description: This is a mouth-watering and delicious vegetarian dish made with spinach, paneer (Indian cottage cheese), green peas, and a very special and fresh spice blend from East 2 West supply. This is a dish that everyone loves

title: Dahi (Yogurt) Chicken
Description: This is a non-veg spicy, tangy, and very flavorful chicken dish pairs perfectly with white rice or roti. Boneless chicken thigh is prepared with plain yogurt and fresh, delicious, flavorful spices from East 2 West Supply. These ingredients are cooked to tender perfection. A must-try!

title: Chicken Biryani
Description: This is a non-veg spicy, tangy, and very flavorful chicken dish pairs perfectly with white rice or roti. Boneless chicken thigh is prepared with plain yogurt and fresh, delicious, flavorful spices from East 2 West Supply. These ingredients are cooked to tender perfection. A must-try!
